{"word":"Sadducees","slug":"sadducees","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Sadducees</b> A sect of the Jews.<br/> Rebuked by John the Baptist<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=3&verse=9'>Mat 3:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=3&verse=9'>Luk 3:9</a><br/> Reject the doctrine of the resurrection<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=22&verse=34'>Mat 22:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=12&verse=27'>Mar 12:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=20&verse=40'>Luk 20:40</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=23&verse=8'>Act 23:8</a><br/> Jesus warns His disciples against<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=16&verse=12'>Mat 16:12</a><br/> Persecute the apostles<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=4&verse=3'>Act 4:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=44&chapter=5&verse=33'>Act 5:33</a>"}]}